            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Combine your<strong> curry powder</strong> with <strong>half</strong> your <strong>roasted garlic paste</strong>, <strong>half</strong> your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> in a bowl</p><p>Add your <strong>salmon fillet[s]</strong> and combine until fully coated</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1986.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1986.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1986.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
