            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1986.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1986.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated salmon fillet[s]</strong>, skin-side down to the pan</p><p>Cook for 5-6 min on each side or until cooked through – this is your <strong>tandoori salmon</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked when it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
